This box is not 100%, but it&#39;s ok.  It&#39;s AM/FM linear sweep, but  hesitates 
on part of the sweep.  I&#39;ve attached audio, you will see what i  mean.

All my boxes are different, this is a 12-589 conversion box with adjustable 
 sweep.  I used a different circuit and it does cover the whole band, but  
has that stutter in the sweep and i can&#39;t figure out why.

My line of boxes are ok, but it&#39;s just a copy of what frank has been doing  
for 10 years.  I&#39;m asking $60 plus shipping.  

If someone wants to give it a shot, i think the price is reasonable  
enough.  Even less than i paid for the parts.

-Steve H.



